{"tid":1658291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警世] 勿分化南亞撚","createTime":"2019-10-16T12:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:21:33.000Z","uid":205376,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2a68a10a0e9e843e70233806a4c35ee85d8896","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"唔好被帶風向<br />\n香港人入面都有一堆仆街一堆黑狗<br />\n對事勿對人"},{"pid":"b16417673b68b075abd34feae09bc4d30c978d79","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1699c7a30625a42545837621b77d862511388f5d","tid":1658291,"uid":71458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:46:07.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n但咁你就唔好叫人南亞撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787cb21605808e91d499de4a1bf2bb2c7d744bae","tid":1658291,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"好多毛帶風向話要裝修南亞，咪亂嚟佢哋係收錢外判工認錢唔認人。<br />\n<br />\n要搞就一定搞出面請南亞做嘢嗰個黑社會，邊撚個字頭咁濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e51f8dad7568072f923d4a249f22ea22d731079","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0b530347b505472cd035e557ec8bad8da3d056a0","tid":1658291,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"720c6aacde8186ba058fb454d47703445f0988cc","tid":1658291,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16417673b68b075abd34feae09bc4d30c978d79","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"只有左狗先沬黑南亞<br />\n真本土燃係最歡迎非支那籍香港人<br />\n例如喬寶寶同利君雅<br />\n因為佢地證明左香港人唔一定支那籍<br />\n另一點同法例有關<br />\n係基本法本身剝奪左南亞人有支那籍既權利<br />\n明明南亞係有藏南地區血統可以用藏族人自居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228c3d0a06b6db71b54865516295ecc09f11b54c","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"242701da46f3a97400739afdd583fd373a0004de","tid":1658291,"uid":21253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"53b0f7cae27b3ad78aeb8fea623f7c1a353085d7","tid":1658291,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5397919386c80dcda5a0ce792050eefe98bf7ca9","tid":1658291,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"我地既敵人跟本就唔係南亞，對準政府先係正確"},{"pid":"968d9685fe5d4fc135f0cc85cf553572c86fc806","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n唔好racial discrimination"},{"pid":"96f9c5520bf0adc532dc9a3497e437fb6122abbe","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3cd85f73659f7c2c93635f4c5a70992c232e737a","tid":1658291,"uid":325884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔使唔使開十幾個post講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集中一兩個講就夠啦，仲要搞分化，大把南亞係自己友黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff2c9044785f754ee64d4684a15ef5035186330","tid":1658291,"uid":285165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多南亞人都係自己人<br />\n唔好殺錯良民"},{"pid":"2f4361c5f40ce48d71ed2d3323c54e717c4fe821","tid":1658291,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"49e2a8ededba8aaaf17ffc6857123cdeda56abdc","tid":1658291,"uid":295863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"嗰班連登分化撚根本唔係香港人，懷疑佢地係大陸五毛狗！！<br />\n愛香港、、以香港為家、捍衛香港價值嘅就係香港人，香港人點會想將場運動變左做種族歧視咁嘅議題、乜野國際形象都冇晒啦"},{"pid":"3030f73e8372c5a511502fa5b1ff83ec8a225aee","tid":1658291,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"南亞撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}